{"_path":"/resident/r012","_dir":"resident","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"借鏡林口, 探索如何強化A7重劃區的環境清潔 - 環保志工篇","description":null,"image":"/images/resident/r012-02.jpeg","sequence":12,"category":"環保","place":"A7重劃區","author":"社區網站","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 "},{"name":"og:title","content":"社區網站-地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-07-23T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"借鏡林口-探索如何強化-a7-重劃區的環境清潔-環保志工篇"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"借鏡林口, 探索如何強化 A7 重劃區的環境清潔 - 環保志工篇"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本篇是借助林口的網路資訊, 希望探索如何強化 A7 重劃區的環境清潔。希望有網友能提供更多的建言, 匯總成為我們努力的方向。\n希望有議員能 探討： 市府環保局作業流程改善 - 環保局作業篇"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"檢討林口在環保志工的作業是否可以成為借鏡！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"市府的支持及鼓勵"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"市府的支持及鼓勵"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"市府對環保志工的支持"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/ntpclowcarbon/posts/pfbid031Zi2etcQUek6hXw9gtfkpddAcFJawB8e7qf2RTRx29GZJU5LeXVfkCLost8oxbG2l?rdid=JhPfzXtlCdBgtv9X"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"新北 i 環保 2024/06/25"}]},{"type":"text","value":": 新北政府對志工的經費補助: 新北市從 114 年起每人每年環保志工經費 1 千元調至 2 千 1 百元"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"平日除了清潔隊員維護市容外，新北市還有一群強大環保志工他們的工作包山包海，像是撿廢棄菸頭, 清除狗便, 清除積水容器, 資源回收等，無論刮風下雨甚至風災過後，環保志工都在默默地維護家園環境因此為了感謝志工們的付出，侯友宜市長宣布 114 年起每人每年環保志工經費 1 千元調至 2 千 1 百元多虧有他們的辛勤努力新北市才能連續 10 年獲得最乾淨城市殊榮。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"新北市府對志工的激勵做法"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.epd.ntpc.gov.tw/Article/Info?ID=11361"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「113 年度新北市環保志(義)工群英會」競賽"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n競賽項目："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n正賽：「環保金頭腦」、「資源分類王」、「資源灌籃高手」及「清掃接力賽」等 4 項環境部指定競賽。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n趣味競賽：環保選邊站。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"各項競賽獎勵方式，說明如下："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(一) 冠軍隊伍：獲新臺幣 1 萬元獎勵金及獎狀 1 面(全國賽新北市代表隊)。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(二) 亞軍隊伍：獲新臺幣 8 仟元獎勵金及獎狀 1 面。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(三) 季軍隊伍：獲新臺幣 5 仟元獎勵金及獎狀 1 面。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(四) 其餘名次：獲新臺幣 1 仟元獎勵金及感謝狀 1 面。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/yfhQ9G2eg2fueiwZ/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市環保志工群英會 "}]},{"type":"text","value":":"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"#環境清掃志工 清除約 23 萬公斤垃圾！ 固定每月第 2 個週六，於街道上維護桃園市容。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n#河川巡守志工 確實監測水質！ 已經執行水質監測超過 800 次以上，並巡檢超過 5,000 次。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n#海岸巡護志工 每月固定淨灘！ 每月辦理 2 次淨灘活動，清除超過 3 萬公斤的垃圾。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n#環境教育志工 辦理百場講座！ 辦理環境教育宣講將近 260 場次，服務約 8 萬名民眾。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"希望 A7 重劃區各里里長也能 用數據說明, A7 環境志工的 具體貢獻！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一, 環保志工服務項目"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.bas.ntpc.gov.tw/userfiles/1180700/files/19.pdf"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"新北環保志工概況"}]},{"type":"text","value":":"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n環保志工的服務項目如下："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(一) 環境改造:協助轄內社區街道巷弄髒亂點消除、環境綠美化、巡查勸導等工作。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(二) 協助或宣導居民做好社區轄內一般廢棄物處理與垃圾分類減量、資源回收等環境清理工作。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(三) 協助發生天然災害地區之環境復原及清理搶救工作。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(四) 協助環保政策之教育宣導、講習等活動及擔任環境污染之監督通報工作。\n(五) 環境維護需要時，運用單位協調或調度各小隊進行相關活動協助。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(六) 其它(視各運用單位需要服務之項目訂定)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"二, 環保志工招募訓練"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n本市環保志工訓練課程係依據志願服務法第 9 條規定略以，「為提昇志願服務工作"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n品質，保障受服務者之權益，志願服務運用單位應對志工辦理下列教育訓練：一、基礎訓練。二、特殊訓練。」，規劃課程說明如圖一："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r012-03.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r012-03.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"居民的參與"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"居民的參與"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"table","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"thead","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"區域別"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"總人口"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"志願服務隊數"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"志願服務人數"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"志工人數占比"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tbody","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2,281,464"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1,937"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"102,554"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"4.5%"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"新北市"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3,995,551"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1,415"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"154,060"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3.9%"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市環境教育全球資訊網 2023/11/09:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"張善政市長表示，桃園市的環保志工人數高達 3 萬 8 千多人，榮居全國之冠，幾乎全國每 7 位環保志工，就有 1 位是桃園市環保志工；而環保志工在市民中的比例，也是六都第一，大約每 1,000 位桃園市民中就有 16 位是環保志工，環保志工隊數也是連年成長，有越來越多的市民加入環保的行列，顯示桃園市民朋友對於環境保護的重視，並且願意身體力行來從事志願服務。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"註; 需要統計 A7 居民參與比例！ 尤其是 樂善里, 長庚里, 文化里 的環保志工中, A7 重劃區的參與比例？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r012-04.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r012-04.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"全區環保作業整合"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"全區環保作業整合"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"林口區行政里的作業整合, 值得 A7 重劃區借鏡。將 A7 的四個里作責任分工 同步作業！ 也希望能 A7 重劃區整體規劃, 將所有區域責任分工給個社區。 由社區管委會協助作業, 如社區周邊應該由社區物業能承擔公有街道上清潔責任。\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r012-05.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r012-05.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"強化機械作業"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"強化機械作業"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"觀察林口區 採用吹風機將樹葉集中後由志工收集, 效率很高。而 A7 重劃區的志工多數仍採用人工撿拾或掃把清掃。 如果能使用吹風機集中, 再採用華亞科技園區的機械化掃街車協助效能將會大幅增強。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r012-06.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r012-06.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n林口的吹風機集中樹葉！\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r012-07.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r012-07.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nA7 重劃區的人工作業"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"企業及熱心居民的主動認養"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"企業及熱心居民的主動認養"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/xsW49BCJMUgrSMEz/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"林口大家庭 2024/06/30"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 居民的主動認養 區域環境整潔, 在林口有喜樂大姐給我們做了最好的示範。 多數髒亂點都在商場如全聯或便利店附近, 希望連鎖企業能發揮 ESG 精神認養店家附近的環境整潔。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r012-08.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r012-08.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"寄望里長議員的推動"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"寄望里長/議員的推動"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"希望 A7 重劃區能以整合的形式建立區域環境整潔工作團隊。 議員的協助下讓四位里長能同步環保作業, 擴大招募 A7 重劃區居民參與環保志工。並將志工作業有效率的分配到 每週一次。 A7 整合環保團隊與所有社區主委直接建立聯繫, 讓居民共同參與。 A7 重劃區的環境清潔要做的比林口還要好！！"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"借鏡林口-探索如何強化-a7-重劃區的環境清潔-環保志工篇","depth":2,"text":"借鏡林口, 探索如何強化 A7 重劃區的環境清潔 - 環保志工篇"},{"id":"市府的支持及鼓勵","depth":2,"text":"市府的支持及鼓勵"},{"id":"居民的參與","depth":2,"text":"居民的參與"},{"id":"全區環保作業整合","depth":2,"text":"全區環保作業整合"},{"id":"強化機械作業","depth":2,"text":"強化機械作業"},{"id":"企業及熱心居民的主動認養","depth":2,"text":"企業及熱心居民的主動認養"},{"id":"寄望里長議員的推動","depth":2,"text":"寄望里長/議員的推動"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:resident:r012.md","_source":"content","_file":"resident/r012.md","_extension":"md"}